 - upssched.txt: document the required PIPEFN and LOCKFN variables

   (Cristian Rigamonti) [Alioth Patch #302107]

Fri Sep 30 20:38:09 UTC 2005 / Arnaud Quette <aquette.dev@gmail.com>

